data.description: Welcome to this spacious and charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence nestled in the delightful Crown Manor community. Revel in the high ceilings of the two-story foyer, a generously sized family room seamlessly connecting to the breakfast area and well-appointed kitchen.    Around the corner, discover a walk-in pantry, a dedicated dining room, and a separate living room or office space. Ascend to the 2nd level to find an ample owner's ensuite with room for a sitting area, a double vanity, and a spacious walk-in closet. On the opposite side, three additional bedrooms offer versatility for guest rooms, offices, or hobbies.    Step outside to a beautifully proportioned backyard, providing an ideal backdrop for outdoor gatherings, lush greenery, recreational space, and endless creative possibilities. Don't let this spacious gem slip away—seize the opportunity before it's too late!
